  <h1 class="gd-h1">Avalanche Safety for Heliskiing</h1>
  <p class="gd-lede">Avalanche safety is the <strong>foundation of every serious heliski operation</strong>, and understanding how it works &mdash; the kit, the knowledge and the professional system behind it &mdash; makes you a safer, more confident guest. This guide explains the essentials honestly, without false reassurance, before you browse <a href="/packages">packages</a> or read about <a href="/iceland">Iceland</a>.</p>
</div></section>
